{"parse":{"title":"Play! Pok\u00e9mon Prize Pack Series Two (TCG)","pageid":283533,"wikitext":{"*":"{{ExpansionPrevNext | prev=Play! Pok\u00e9mon Prize Pack Series One | next=Play! Pok\u00e9mon Prize Pack Series Three}}\n{{TCGPromoInfobox\n|setname=Play! Pok\u00e9mon Prize Pack Series Two\n|symbol=no\n|cards=154\n|period=January 19, 2023\n|logo=Play! Pok\u00e9mon Prize Pack Series Two logo.png\n}}\n\n'''Play! Pok\u00e9mon Prize Pack Series Two''' is a series of promotional cards released on January 19, 2023 through [[Play! Pok\u00e9mon|Pok\u00e9mon Organized Play]] events or affiliated products. This set features 154 specifically selected cards from the {{TCG|Battle Styles}} expansion through {{TCG|Brilliant Stars}} in addition to {{TCG|SWSH Black Star Promos}}, some items from the {{TCG|Sword & Shield}} base set, and Brilliant Stars Print {{TCG|Energy card|Basic Energy cards}}. All cards retained their original set number, but are marked with the Play! Pok\u00e9mon logo. Each Booster pack contains 6 cards.\n\n==Card list==\nTPCi sublty published an official Card List on 24 October, 2023.<ref>[https://www.pokemon.com/static-assets/content-assets/cms2/pdf/trading-card-game/checklist/prize_pack_series_2_web_cardlist_en.pdf Pok\u00e9mon TCG: Prize Pack\u2014Series Two Card List]</ref>\n\n{{Setlist/header|title=Play! Pok\u00e9mon Prize Pack Series Two|bordercol={{Tcg Psychic color}}|tablecol={{Unknown color}}|cellcol={{Tcg Fairy color}}|textcolor=000000|rarity=yes|symbol=no|promo=yes}}\n{{Setlist/entry|SWSH111|E|[[Galarian Rapidash V (SWSH Promo 111)|Galarian Rapidash]]{{TCGV}}|Psychic||None|Standard Set Foil}}\n{{Setlist/entry|SWSH149|E|[[Flareon V (SWSH Promo 149)|Flareon]]{{TCGV}}|Fire||None|Standard Set Foil}}\n{{Setlist/entry|SWSH150|E|[[Vaporeon V (SWSH Promo 150)|Vaporeon]]{{TCGV}}|Water||None|Standard Set Foil}}\n{{Setlist/entry|SWSH151|E|[[Jolteon V (SWSH Promo 151)|Jolteon]]{{TCGV}}|Lightning||None|Standard Set Foil}}\n{{Setlist/entry|SWSH195|F|[[Leafeon VSTAR